These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
Flower: orchid, lily
Food: cucumber, strawberry
Transport: roller, taxi
1. Food:cucumber is on the right of Transport:roller##1
2. Flower:lily is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Flower   | lily    | orchid |
| Food         | strawberry | cucumber    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
